            "icon_title": "Grayanotoxin II (GTX II)",
            "icon_description": "Grayanotoxin II reduces the natural rhythm of the sinoatrial node by alteri-ng the cell membrane’s permeability to sodium ions and is considered the least toxic form of all grayanotoxins. It requires larger doses to produce si-milar effects, resulting in milder symptoms that develop more slowly and have temporary effects.",
